**Summary:** This documentation describes the Amplitude-Segment integration for syncing behavioral cohorts from Amplitude to Segment using Segment's writeKey authentication, enabling cohort data to be used with ad networks and marketing tools through Segment identify calls that set cohort membership as True/False user traits.

